 Dakle, vi optužujete, dakle, govorite protiv preljuba.

324
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:22,000
 Ali ne mrzite, ne govorite protiv onoga ko čini preljub.

325
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:27,000
 So you have to separate the devil from the sinner.

326
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:33,000
 Morate odvojiti džavla od grešnika.

327
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:37,000
 Protestantism is the work of Satan.

