337
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:38,000
 Nego ga je doveo Duh Sveti.

338
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:41,000
 To je milost.

339
00:43:41,000 --> 00:43:51,000
 Zato crkva moli za obraćanje svih odvojenih kršćana.

340
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:55,000
